author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Four years ago Epic games took Apple to court over Fortnite and now we're looking at the culmination. Epic got a massive victory, Apple got exposed for lying and a bunch of gamers get access to one of the biggest games on their phones once again and all it took was Apple taking the biggest loss of the year so far. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Apple Just Got Completely Destroyed In Court...
